name: Ise_Pev_Trin
content:
Ise Pev Trin was a lead design analyst of an unknown species from Iokath who worked with master designer Vel Jyc Boer. Ise Pev Trin worked on Test environment Z17AX558.
Ise Pev Trin is mentioned in Star Wars: The Old Republic: Knights of the Eternal Throne in the codex entry 'History of Iokath: Entry 2'.
